      "title": "How power cuts are implemented today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Accordingly, in zones A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, ST, U, V, W, one hour and 40 minutes during day and night. A power cut will be in effect for an hour and 20 minutes.",
        "In addition, there will be a two-and-a-half-hour power cut in Colombo business areas from 6 am to 8.30 am.",
        "Also, power cut will be implemented for 3 hours from 5.30 am to 8.30 am in M, N, O, X, Y, Z zones."
      ],
